<ratddesc verstatus="ver"><title><acronym><def>Record Of Applicable
Technical Directives Description</def><term>RATD</term></acronym></title>
<para>This element contains a list of applicable technical directives.
This is where an<acronym><def>Engineering Change Proposal</def><term>ECP</term>
</acronym> or an <acronym><def>Engineering Change Notice</def><term>ECN</term>
</acronym>would be listed. An ECP or ECN is generated by the engineering
staff of a aircraft or system manufacture for the purpose of modifying
an existing aircraft or system.</para>
<ratd>
<ratdentry><typeno>TYPENO Element</typeno><date>DATE</date><title>TITLE</title>
<ecpno> ECPNO</ecpno><dateinc>DATEINC</dateinc><remarks>REMARKS</remarks>
</ratdentry>
